00:27:57.460 --> 00:27:58.720
You deserve a break.

00:27:58.720 --> 00:28:01.930
Go and take a break and reward
yourself with that Kit Kat.

00:28:01.930 --> 00:28:05.650
Or Coca-Cola-- life tastes good.

00:28:05.650 --> 00:28:07.240
Go and celebrate
your life by drinking

00:28:07.240 --> 00:28:09.880
our carbonated sugary pop drink.

00:28:09.880 --> 00:28:13.690
Or Pringles-- once you pop,
you can't stop, basically

00:28:13.690 --> 00:28:17.680
normalizing it to eat a
whole tub in one sitting.

00:28:17.680 --> 00:28:19.580
Or maybe the worst
culprit of them all,

00:28:19.580 --> 00:28:22.750
McDonald's-- are your
kids misbehaving again?

00:28:22.750 --> 00:28:24.475
Swing by and get
them a Happy Meal.

00:28:24.475 --> 00:28:26.090
That will put a
smile on their face

00:28:26.090 --> 00:28:27.760
