00:33:11.140 --> 00:33:13.890
Another really common thing
is if we weren't allowed it

00:33:13.890 --> 00:33:17.140
at home as kids,
then when we grow up

00:33:17.140 --> 00:33:19.360
and we're suddenly adults
and free and liberated,

00:33:19.360 --> 00:33:20.770
we're like, oh, my God.

00:33:20.770 --> 00:33:22.190
I can eat it now.

00:33:22.190 --> 00:33:23.970
I'm allowed to eat
whatever I want.

00:33:23.970 --> 00:33:29.430
It symbolizes this rebellion and
this freedom and independence.

00:33:29.430 --> 00:33:35.620
So food is parallel to our life.

00:33:35.620 --> 00:33:37.660
So our relationship
with food can

00:33:37.660 --> 00:33:41.170
be this kind of comfort,
this emotional tool.

00:33:41.170 --> 00:33:42.700
But it can also be pleasure.

00:33:42.700 --> 00:33:45.460
And I think when we get
sucked into diet land,

00:33:45.460 --> 00:33:47.230
we forget that we're
allowed to receive

00:33:47.230 --> 00:33:48.520
pleasure and joy from food.

00:33:48.520 --> 00:33:53.740
It's allowed to be a completely
celebratory experience.

00:33:53.740 --> 00:33:56.080
And a good question
to ask yourself

00:33:56.080 --> 00:33:59.580
when you're turning to food is,
am I using this to celebrate?

00:33:59.580 --> 00:34:02.170
Or am I using it to escape?

00:34:02.170 --> 00:34:06.010
Because often, we're actually
trying to push down a feeling.

00:34:06.010 --> 00:34:08.710
So our relationship with
food is a reflection

00:34:08.710 --> 00:34:10.210
of our relationship
with life, which

00:34:10.210 --> 00:34:12.639
means-- you know that saying,
how you do one thing is

00:34:12.639 --> 00:34:14.920
how you do everything?

00:34:14.920 --> 00:34:17.889
So it's kind of like how you do
food is often how you do life.

00:34:17.889 --> 00:34:20.409
So if you are a perfectionist
around your food,

00:34:20.409 --> 00:34:22.989
you're probably also a
perfectionist in your life.

00:34:22.989 --> 00:34:25.650
If you are controlling
around food,

00:34:25.650 --> 00:34:28.030
you're probably also
controlling in life.

00:34:28.030 --> 00:34:30.690
And who's an
all-or-nothing person?

00:34:30.690 --> 00:34:32.810
Anyone here totally
all-or-nothing?

00:34:32.810 --> 00:34:35.100
So if you're
all-or-nothing with food,

00:34:35.100 --> 00:34:37.270
you're probably
also all-or-nothing

00:34:37.270 --> 00:34:39.250
in your life, in
your relationships,

00:34:39.250 --> 00:34:41.510
in your job or projects.

00:34:41.510 --> 00:34:46.300
And who here would say
that they are a fast eater?

00:34:46.300 --> 00:34:46.851
everyone.

