00:34:50.090 --> 00:34:51.539
So if you're a
fast eater, you're

00:34:51.539 --> 00:34:53.080
probably also going
through your life

00:34:53.080 --> 00:34:56.350
quite fast, which is why
it's difficult to get people

00:34:56.350 --> 00:34:58.072
to slow down their eating.

00:34:58.072 --> 00:34:59.530
Because it's
basically like saying,

00:34:59.530 --> 00:35:01.000
slow down your life pace.

00:35:01.000 --> 00:35:04.300
Do you also drive your car
quite fast if you drive?

00:35:04.300 --> 00:35:07.150
Do you go through your life
quite fast in other areas?

00:35:07.150 --> 00:35:08.200
Yeah.

00:35:08.200 --> 00:35:09.940
So what this means
is when we are

00:35:09.940 --> 00:35:13.000
able to heal ourself with food,
we can also heal our life.

00:35:13.000 --> 00:35:18.610
And if we're able to enjoy a
more intuitive way of eating,

00:35:18.610 --> 00:35:20.260
it means we're more
likely to enjoy

00:35:20.260 --> 00:35:23.270
an intuitive way of living.

00:35:23.270 --> 00:35:25.630
So I always say intuitive
eating paves the way

00:35:25.630 --> 00:35:27.010
for intuitive living.

00:35:27.010 --> 00:35:31.190
When I was able to learn how
to really listen to my body,

00:35:31.190 --> 00:35:34.150
I was also able to learn
how to listen to my gut.

00:35:34.150 --> 00:35:36.610
I was able to learn how
to listen to my intuition.

00:35:36.610 --> 00:35:40.250
I realized that the
two went hand in hand.

00:35:40.250 --> 00:35:41.687
So a lot of people
think that when

00:35:41.687 --> 00:35:43.270
they're going to
listen to their body,

00:35:43.270 --> 00:35:45.020
they think that their
body is just telling

00:35:45.020 --> 00:35:46.332
them to eat all kinds of junk.

00:35:46.332 --> 00:35:47.540
And it's simply not the case.

00:35:47.540 --> 00:35:50.080
So I want to explain to
you guys-- just to finish--

00:35:50.080 --> 00:35:53.560
the difference between
your real hunger

00:35:53.560 --> 00:35:55.510
and your emotional cravings.

00:35:55.510 --> 00:35:58.690
So real hunger comes on
very gradually, slowly.

00:35:58.690 --> 00:36:00.190
And you feel it here, right?

00:36:00.190 --> 00:36:01.630
You feel it in the stomach.

00:36:01.630 --> 00:36:04.720
And it gives you the
time and that patience

00:36:04.720 --> 00:36:06.430
to go, what am I hungry for?

00:36:06.430 --> 00:36:10.210
What am I going to choose
to nourish my body?

00:36:10.210 --> 00:36:13.690
Whereas an emotional craving is
actually a psychological need.

00:36:13.690 --> 00:36:16.270
And it comes on very
fast in the mind.

00:36:16.270 --> 00:36:17.490
And it's that urge.

00:36:17.490 --> 00:36:18.610
It's that impulse.

00:36:18.610 --> 00:36:22.150
And it usually fixates on
one particular kind of food.

00:36:22.150 --> 00:36:24.350
So it comes on really fast.

00:36:24.350 --> 00:36:27.265
And if you don't check yourself,
you kind of glaze over.

00:36:27.265 --> 00:36:28.640
And you become
this zombie state.

00:36:28.640 --> 00:36:29.920
And before you know it,
you've eaten something.

00:36:29.920 --> 00:36:31.725
And you don't even
know how you got there.

00:36:31.725 --> 00:36:33.100
If we were doing
that with drugs,

00:36:33.100 --> 00:36:34.766
it would be a pretty
big problem, right?

00:36:34.766 --> 00:36:36.910
But we do that with food a lot.

00:36:36.910 --> 00:36:40.389
So when we have those
psychological cravings,

00:36:40.389 --> 00:36:42.430
what we're actually craving
is something deeper--

00:36:42.430 --> 00:36:45.220
usually love,
usually connection.

00:36:45.220 --> 00:36:48.610
And all of those things
that we are craving we

00:36:48.610 --> 00:36:49.960
can give to ourselves.

00:36:49.960 --> 00:36:52.420
We can never truly
get those needs

00:36:52.420 --> 00:36:57.400
met from someone else, a
food, a drink, a substance,

00:36:57.400 --> 00:37:00.430
social media, all of these
kind of external things.

00:37:00.430 --> 00:37:02.800
It's a way in which we
try to fill ourselves up

00:37:02.800 --> 00:37:06.340
from the outside in rather
than filling ourselves

00:37:06.340 --> 00:37:09.430
up from the inside
out in fulfillment

00:37:09.430 --> 00:37:12.190
and living a truly full-up life.

00:37:12.190 --> 00:37:13.460
So thank you.

00:37:13.460 --> 00:37:16.390
