00:38:11.260 --> 00:38:12.640
from intuitive eating.

00:38:12.640 --> 00:38:17.000
And you can do one without
the other and vice versa.

00:38:17.000 --> 00:38:20.290
So I would say that the
body positive movement

00:38:20.290 --> 00:38:21.850
is a movement in itself.

00:38:21.850 --> 00:38:23.650
And the people that
started that have

00:38:23.650 --> 00:38:26.470
their own definition
of what that is

00:38:26.470 --> 00:38:28.130
and what they stand for.

00:38:28.130 --> 00:38:32.020
But you can decide that for you
to be positive for your body,

00:38:32.020 --> 00:38:34.780
for you to show your body
love, means to not have things

00:38:34.780 --> 00:38:36.470
that don't agree with it.

00:38:36.470 --> 00:38:39.850
So for example, I consider
myself to be body positive

00:38:39.850 --> 00:38:43.270
because I do positive
things for my body,

00:38:43.270 --> 00:38:45.850
although I'm not a part,
necessarily, of that movement.

00:38:45.850 --> 00:38:48.370
And the roots of
it obviously were

00:38:48.370 --> 00:38:52.180
different from where I'm sat.

00:38:52.180 --> 00:38:55.270
But if doing a positive
thing for your body

00:38:55.270 --> 00:38:58.870
is not having certain foods
that don't agree with it,

00:38:58.870 --> 00:39:00.190
then that's absolutely great.

00:39:00.190 --> 00:39:04.330
I don't think intuitive
eating is about just

00:39:04.330 --> 00:39:06.130
eating rubbish all the time.

00:39:06.130 --> 00:39:09.140
I think it's about noticing what
feels good and what doesn't.

00:39:09.140 --> 00:39:10.870
And that's definitely
something that I've

00:39:10.870 --> 00:39:11.911
learned along my journey.

00:39:11.911 --> 00:39:14.230
Because I thought that
going into intuitive eating

00:39:14.230 --> 00:39:16.510
would mean that I would
just gain loads of weight

00:39:16.510 --> 00:39:19.600
and would just sit around
eating donuts and ice cream

00:39:19.600 --> 00:39:21.430
and all kinds of
cereal for dinner

00:39:21.430 --> 00:39:22.910
and all this kind of stuff.

00:39:22.910 --> 00:39:24.290
And it's not what happened.

00:39:24.290 --> 00:39:26.800
I think initially, there
might be a boomerang phase

00:39:26.800 --> 00:39:28.820
where you're just like
oh, my God, freedom.

00:39:28.820 --> 00:39:30.736
But then after that,
what happens is you start

00:39:30.736 --> 00:39:32.970
to recognize what feels
good and what doesn't.

00:39:32.970 --> 00:39:34.720
And you start to notice
that, actually, it

00:39:34.720 --> 00:39:37.580
feels really good to have
this amount of vegetables.

00:39:37.580 --> 00:39:40.010
And it feels really good to
have meat or to not have meat.

00:39:40.010 --> 00:39:43.090
And it feels really good to have
gluten or to not have gluten.

00:39:43.090 --> 00:39:46.480
And it's really about you taking
your power back around food

00:39:46.480 --> 00:39:49.030
and not thinking that it
has to look a certain way.

00:39:49.030 --> 00:39:51.964
It's about you becoming
the boss of your own body.

